{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"看到的，听到的，感到的","authors":["臧克家"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":5,"day":8}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到的，听到的，感到的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想写篇诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想写篇诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌颂南下“动员令”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百万兵马已渡过长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等不及我的诗句完成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×          ×          ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想写篇诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌颂解放贵池和铜陵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江阴下了，南京下了，杭州又下了……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的诗句跟不上大军的行动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×        ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想写篇诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表达心里的高兴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拾起笔来又放下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心，象大海上起了暴风！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃小米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿粗衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千锤百炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢一般结实！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×          ×          ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘掉了自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一条牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哞哞的替老百姓“拉犁！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的报纸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的报纸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给人民服务；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不给资产阶级的“趣味”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"服务。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×          ×        ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号召生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号召支前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好的表扬，坏的批判！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×          ×        ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一条消息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都负责——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白的纸，黑的字！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆炸女英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年纪不过二十岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说着一口山东话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋地雷时你那么大胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众人面前却有点羞答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“只作了这么一饤点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算不了什么。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身子一歪，你笑了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑得多么天真呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听英雄们报告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，战斗英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，劳动英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，爆炸英雄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×          ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去，她是童养媳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是农民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是木匠出身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×          ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们报告自己的身世，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象述说一段古代史；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们描写战争的经历，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有声有色象“传奇”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×          ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本来是一个大字也不识，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，蚂蚁般爬满一本子；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本来人面前张不开口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，涛浪似的满嘴的文化名词。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×          ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有什么比这更丰富？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有什么比这更生动？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它使教授们抱愧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它使作家脸上有羞色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不是共产党来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们怎么能到得这样的地方？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是毛主席领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们怎么能对诸位先生演讲？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个话讲完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家巴掌拍得响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个走下来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸前排着“毛泽东勋章”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“北平入城式”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我两眼热泪横流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“天津解放战”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我直瞪着眼，气也不敢抽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心里得到了一个保证："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军，有摧毁一切敌人的英勇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“民主东北”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“安东工业林业生产”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"繁荣新中国的一幅小影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慢慢的慢慢的在眼前扩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}